tag.description: Shagbark Hickory. Probably var. australis (southern shagbark hickory or Carolina hickory). Good for smoking or firewood. Look for downed branches and city trimming. Crews often leave firewood on the parkway. Large branch fell on 19 Apr 16. Diseased.
